  </div>
  <div class="hru-right">
    <div class="field field-title"><h2>Not Optional Anymore - Canada commits to signing Optional Protocol!</h2></div>
    <div class="field field-summary"><p>Foreign Minister StÃ©phane Dion announces Canada&#039;s commitment to sign torture treaty!</p></div>
